# Predicate lambda passed to a counting HOF.
*count_if(xs as Vec of i64, pred as (i64) returns bool) returns i64
    n is 0
    i is 0
    while i < xs.length
        if pred(xs.get(i))
            n is n + 1
        i is i + 1
    n

*main
    xs is vec()
    i is 0
    while i < 20
        xs.push(i)
        i is i + 1
    log count_if(xs, |n as i64| n mod 2 equals 0)
    log count_if(xs, |n as i64| n > 14)
